• The Vetplantfees (Succulent Festival) hosted by the Calitzdorp Succulent Society to showcase many of South Africa’s beautiful and rare succulents together with succulents from all over the world. A range of activities to discover the world of succulents – workshops, veldwalks, expert talks, etc. Contact: info@vetplant.co.za. More on www.vetplant.co.za • Eerste De Rust en Meiringspoortfees. Inlig­ting: Willie Immelman (082 952 2001 / wduikergans @yahoo.com) of Callie Burger (082 455 5487).